summary: AN ORDINANCE granting permission to H. O. Crane to improve the North/South Alley in Block 63, Rainier Beach Addition from its junction with the East-West Alley in said Block to approximately 90 feet south thereof, being a portion of the north-south alley in the block bounded by Rainier Avenue South, 57th Avenue South, South Fletcher Street and 56th Avenue South, by grading and otherwise improving the same, at his own cost and expense.
